  All but the `PositionalBinding` property are inherited from the → Microsoft/dot-net/namespaces-classes/System/Management/Automation/CmdletCommonMetadataAttribute[`CmdletCommonMetadataAttribute`]
  class.

}

sa:
  The influence of the `cmdletBinding` attribute on the → Windows/PowerShell/language/variable/automatic/PsCmdLet[PowerShell automatic variable `$psCmdLet`].

  PowerShell has the `[cmdLetBinding`] → Windows/PowerShell/language/object/type/accelerators[type accelarator] for `System.Management.Automation.CmdletBinding`.

  → Microsoft/dot-net/namespaces-classes/System/Management/Automation/PagingParameters[`System.Management.Automation.PagingParameters`]
